Version : 2

Limitation : Development will be done on aeroMart code 008.0

Description :  BML is upgraded the payment gateway version 2 which is not compatible with version 1. Currently flyme uses the BML payment gateway. 

Payment flow

The customer clicks the pay button on IBE

aeroMart backend sends the payment initiation request to payment gateway

aeroMart redirects the customer to payment gateway

aeroMart process the redirection response

